				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/accountability" title="View all posts in Accountability" rel="category tag">Accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/articles" title="View all posts in Articles" rel="category tag">Articles</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/big-brother" title="View all posts in Big Brother" rel="category tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/nsa" title="View all posts in NSA" rel="category tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/privacy-2" title="View all posts in Privacy" rel="category tag">Privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/snowden" title="View all posts in Snowden" rel="category tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/technology" title="View all posts in Technology" rel="category tag">Technology</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
