                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>A recent inter­view with James Corbett of the <a href="http://www.corbettreport.com/">Corbett Report</a> on <a href="http://grtv.ca/2013/02/death-privacy-inside-fisaechelon-spy-grid">Global Research <span class="caps">TV</span> </a>dis­cuss­ing issues such as <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foreign_Intelligence_Surveillance_Act"><span class="caps">FISA</span></a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/echelon-redux.html">Ech­elon</a>, and our cul­tural “groom­ing” by the bur­geon­ing sur­veil­lance state:<br />
<iframe src="http://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/mYmc9RqQ8pA" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
