				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/big-brother" rel="tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/copyright" rel="tag">copyright</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cory-doctorow" rel="tag">Cory Doctorow</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/eben-moglen" rel="tag">Eben Moglen</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intellectual-property" rel="tag">intellectual property</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/p2p" rel="tag">P2P</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/technology-2" rel="tag">technology</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/telstra" rel="tag">Telstra</a>			</span>
						
