							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/asteroid-interactive" rel="tag">Asteroid Interactive</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/domain-name" rel="tag">domain name</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/open-source-2" rel="tag">open source</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sander-venema" rel="tag">Sander Venema</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/switzerland" rel="tag">Switzerland</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/using-our-intelligence" rel="tag">using our intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/website" rel="tag">website</a>			</span>
						
